name: UInterchangeAnimationTrackSetNode
doc: Class to represent a set of animation track nodes that share the same frame rate.

methods.name: AddCustomAnimationTrackUid
methods.doc: Add one track dependency to this object.

methods.name: GetCustomAnimationTrackUid
methods.doc: Retrieve one track dependency for this object.

methods.name: GetCustomAnimationTrackUidCount
methods.doc: Retrieve the number of track dependencies for this object.

methods.name: GetCustomAnimationTrackUids
methods.doc: Retrieve the track dependency for this object.

methods.name: GetCustomFrameRate
methods.doc: Get the frame rate for the animations in the level sequence.

methods.name: RemoveCustomAnimationTrackUid
methods.doc: Remove one track dependency from this object.

methods.name: SetCustomFrameRate
methods.doc: Set the frame rate for the animations in the level sequence.
